cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with solving inverse problems in computer vision using generative adversarial networks (GANs) as image priors. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as unsupervised learning and adversarial defense, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves graphics and image processing, which could place it in cs.GR (Computer Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
